title: Veggie's Delight
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Taiwanese, Take-out only
description: Very small take-out only food shop. Sells some deli style sides in addition to some chilled and frozen foods. Offerings usually include steamed buns, noodles, Taiwanese pastries, dumplings, veggie meats, and soybean products. Offers a daily hot lunch box during the week 11am-2:30pm.
